snippet.title: BattleJuice Alchemist Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1384060/BattleJuice_Alchemist/
https://store.epicgames.com/p/battlejuice-alchemist-0b3ffa 

BattleJuice Alchemist is an alchemy RPG where you build and craft your way through Caribou Creek, defying demons in the isometric wilderness. It's out now via Steam Early Access.
